(99, 1, '2020-06-05 22:55:38', '2020-06-05 20:55:38', '<img width=\"640\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1-1024x360.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1-1024x360.jpeg 1024w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1-300x106.jpeg 300w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1-768x270.jpeg 768w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1-850x299.jpeg 850w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tab-narrow-banner-1.jpeg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />											\n			<h3><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 45px; white-space: normal;\">My Books</h1></h3>		\n			<h5><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 26.208px; font-family: Merriweather, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial; margin-top: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Reaching Beyond Boundaries: A Navy SEAL’s Guide to Achieving Anything You’ve Ever Imagined</em></h3></h5>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"448\" src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Reaching-Beyond-Boundaries.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Reaching-Beyond-Boundaries.jpg 300w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Reaching-Beyond-Boundaries-201x300.jpg 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h4><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Reaching-beyond-Boundaries-Achieving-Everything/dp/1510736670\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\">Buy at Amazon.com</a></h4>		\n			<h4>From&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">New York Times</i>&nbsp;bestselling author and Navy SEAL Don Mann and Kraig Becker, advice on how to make your dreams a reality.</h4>		\n			<p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\">For the last decade, decorated Navy SEAL, accomplished athlete, and bestselling author Don Mann has been traveling across the country giving motivational talks and, in the process, inspiring hundreds with the secrets behind his awe-inspiring achievements. In&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Reaching beyond Boundaries</i>, Mann brings his much sought-after wisdom to the page. Chapters include:</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: 25px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The Combat Mindset</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Setting Micro and Macro Goals</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Learning from Failure</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Learning from Success</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">What Navy SEAL Training Taught Me</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Eliminating Excuses</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">It’s Never too Late to Get Started</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">And much more!</li></ul>As an elite Navy SEAL, Mann performed seemingly impossible tasks on a regular basis. Here he details the lessons he learned from his training and shows how the rest of us can apply those teachings to our daily lives in terms of learning to push beyond our internal boundaries and achieve the goals we’ve set for ourselves, both professionally and personally.&nbsp;<i style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit;\">Reaching Beyond Boundaries</i>&nbsp;teaches how to set and conquer both micro- and macro-goals through removing excuses, having the right mindset, and learning from successes and failures.</p>		\n			<h2>With&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\">Reaching Beyond Boundaries</i>&nbsp;you can begin to realize your fullest potential today.</h2>		\n			<h5><h3 id=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 26.208px; font-family: Merriweather, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial; margin-top: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Overcoming Obstacles: A Navy SEAL’s Guide to Beating Adversity and Finding Success</em></h3></h5>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"414\" src=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/overcoming-obstacles.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/overcoming-obstacles.jpg 300w, http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/overcoming-obstacles-217x300.jpg 217w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h2><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Overcoming-Obstacles-Beating-Adversity-Finding/dp/1510745734/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\">Buy at Amazon.com</a></h2>		\n			<p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; white-space: norm